:markdown
  # Switch Fields

  This component is based on the library [Bootstrap Switch](http://www.bootstrap-switch.org/).

  The specific datas for this component are :

  * `status` (**'active'**, 'disabled') : 'active' if not specified
  * `animate` (**true**, false) : true if not specified
  * `on_color` | `off_color` (**primary** | info | success | warning | danger | default)
  * `on_text` | `off_text` (String) : respectively **'ON'** and **'OFF'** if not specified
  * `label_text` (String) : empty if not specified

  Specific options for this component are :

  * `readonly` (true, **false**) : false if not specified
  * `checked` (**true**, false) : true if not specified

  The syntax is :
  `switch_field 'name', { data: argument }, { option: argument }`

- @sections = sections do |s|
  - s.section title: "Switch Field" do
    = example do |e|
      - e.header do
        = switch_field 'examplebasic'
      - e.code do
        switch_field 'examplebasic'
      - e.footer do
        = documentation_link 'Documentation', '#'

  - s.section title: "Status" do
    = example do |e|
      - e.header do
        = switch_field 'examplestatus', { status: 'active' }
        = switch_field 'examplestatus', { status: 'disabled' }
      - e.code do
        switch_field 'examplestatus', { status: 'active' }
        switch_field 'examplestatus', { status: 'disabled' }
      - e.footer do
        = documentation_link 'Documentation', '#'

  - s.section title: "Animate" do
    = example do |e|
